    ou modifiées (@{"CLOSE" LINK CLOSE}, @{"MODIF" LINK MODIF}, @{"LOCK" LINK LOCK}, @{"UNLOCK" LINK UNLOCK}, @{"SAVEALL" LINK SAVEALL}, @{"OBJECTS" LINK OBJECTS}, @{"FONTNAME" LINK FONTNAME},
